### **KEY ARCHITECTURAL DIFFERENCES**

| Aspect | IRC | Nostr |
|--------|-----|-------|
| **Account Model** | Multi-account (per server) | Single/top-level account |
| **Chat Types** | Direct + Group (channels) | Direct only (DMs) |
| **Media Support** | Yes | No (MVP) |
| **Block Streaming** | Supported | Not applicable |
| **Capabilities** | Full protocol support | NIP-04 encrypted DMs |
| **State Management** | Per-account monitor loop | Per-account Nostr bus |
| **Messaging Targets** | Channels (#chan) + nicks | Pubkeys (npub/hex) |
| **Config Scope** | channels.irc.accounts[id] | Top-level channels.nostr |
| **Runtime Extras** | Probing, NickServ, TLS opts | Profile publishing, metrics |

